id: zw_cc_powerlevel
label: PowerLevel Command Class
category: Z-Wave|Command Classes
description: >
  Powerlevel Command Class defines RF transmit power controlling Commands
  useful when installing or testing a network.

  The Commands makes it possible for supporting controllers to set/get
  the RF transmit power level of a node and test specific links between nodes
  with a specific RF transmit power level.

  NOTE: This Command Class is only used in an installation or test situation

package: Z-Wave
quality: production
source:
  - path: protocol/z-wave/ZAF/CommandClasses/PowerLevel/CC_PowerLevel.c
provides:
  - name: zw_cc_powerlevel
requires:
  - name: zw_core
